room_title: Escape room "Escape from 20,000 Leagues" by RED VEIN Escape in Richmond (VA)
room_description: Deep inside the hidden train tunnels of Ashland lies a secret passageway to the Ashland Docks. A first officer from the legendary Nautilus has arrived looking for more navigators on a journey to Atlantis. The missionâ€¦ to observe wild sea life and creatures this ancient civilization has been hiding for centuries. Be vigilant, as there are few very special, but dangerous native aquatic animals along the way. Organize your team of adventurers and explore the watery depths of the Atlantic Ocean! Good luck navigators!
